snippet.title: Way of the Hunter | Showcase Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
The great outdoors await in Way of the Hunter! 

Become the owner of a hunting lodge nestled among gorgeous habitats teeming with wildlife. Discover true to life animals and handle various detailed and highly realistic weapons while you face the challenges of a struggling family business. 

Way of the Hunter is coming to PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S on August 16, 2022.
 
- Links & Info - 
Steam: https://thqn.net/woth-steam
Website: http://wayofthehunter.com 
Discord: https://discord.gg/wayofthehunter
